{"tid":2004218,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得「Legend」呢個字用得太濫 已經冇哂價值","createTime":"2020-05-06T09:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T00:34:04.000Z","uid":165817,"like":36,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"2eaf91f938437436b1576ef91ce7cef6ea90731a","tid":2004218,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T09:50:22.000Z","msg":"Legend即係傳奇<br />\n喺我心目中 傳奇除咗好波之外<br />\n應該要有啲傳奇色彩<br />\n<br />\n好似肥馬咁 場內球王一扭六 場外吸毒死過翻生<br />\n好似C朗咁 由窮小子變球壇首富<br />\n好似碧咸咁 踢波踢到比明星更大名氣<br />\n好似大哨咁 傷完又傷傷完又傷都企返起身<br />\n我諗呢啲冇人反對佢地係legends<br />\n<br />\n但係而家基本上踢波叻少少 喺同一隊效力長少少<br />\n都會俾人叫做傳奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o1E04DH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo1E04DH.jpg&h=cdac9940&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iX98t5m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiX98t5m.jpg&h=ef7f9374&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n33dFb0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn33dFb0.jpg&h=4f0d6366&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wd85wiF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwd85wiF.jpg&h=54e9d845&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fScJ2qj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfScJ2qj.jpg&h=343fed8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CsRVTw1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCsRVTw1.jpg&h=42497e81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗌到冇哂價值 傳奇呢個字已經完全唔矜貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9389848347aa5bec97993268966d66da99eea446","tid":2004218,"uid":27416,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T09:58:29.000Z","msg":"球隊legend 唔同球壇legend<br />\n南華傑志都有各自既legend"},{"pid":"b878bfe0b806b73fc